<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .content {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding: 20px;
        border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .commission-details {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin: 15px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        color: #6c757d;
        font-size: 14px;
        margin-top: 30px;
      }
      .highlight {
        color: #0066cc;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="header">
      <h1>委托提交成功确认</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <p>亲爱的 <span class="highlight"><%= @customer_name %></span>，</p>
      
      <p>感谢您提交约稿委托！我们已经成功收到您的委托申请，以下是您的委托详情：</p>
      
      <div class="commission-details">
        <h3>委托信息</h3>
        <p><strong>委托标题：</strong><%= @commission_title %></p>
        <% if @commission_description.present? %>
          <p><strong>详细描述：</strong></p>
          <p><%= simple_format(@commission_description) %></p>
        <% end %>
        <% if @commission_budget.present? %>
          <p><strong>预算：</strong>¥<%= number_with_delimiter(@commission_budget) %></p>
        <% end %>
        <% if @estimated_delivery_date.present? %>
          <p><strong>预计交付日期：</strong><%= @estimated_delivery_date.strftime('%Y年%m月%d日') %></p>
        <% end %>
        <p><strong>提交时间：</strong><%= @commission.created_at.strftime('%Y年%m月%d日 %H:%M') %></p>
      </div>
      
      <h3>接下来的流程</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>我会在 <strong>24小时内</strong> 回复您的委托申请</li>
        <li>确认委托详情和具体要求</li>
        <li>商定最终的交付时间和费用</li>
        <li>开始创作并定期更新进度</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p>在我更新委托状态之前，您可以自行编辑需求或是删除委托。</p>
      
      <p>再次感谢您的信任！</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>此邮件由系统自动发送，请勿直接回复</p>
      <p>如有疑问，请联系：<a href="mailto:towtyechan@gmail.com">towtyechan@gmail.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>